<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="41" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="41">Culture characters.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="41">Colony originally flat with white fluffy aerial mycelium, becoming greyish mycelium with age, with yellowish-cream conidial drops exuding from the ostioles.</paragraph>
